bdi4jade.plan.planbody

Interface OutputPlanBody

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    ParallelGoalPlanBody, SequentialGoalPlanBody

    public interface OutputPlanBody
    This interface defines that a PlanBody provides output for a goal that is being achieved. These outputs that are properties of the goal may be set during the plan body execution, but this interface defines a method for explicit performing this task of setting outputs.
    Author:
    Ingrid Nunes
